INSERT INTO `hf_local_hometown_reports` VALUES ('9', '1', '【看邻水】加快乡镇道路恢复改造 确保春节期间出行畅通', '1', '2017-03-27 16:46:53', '0', '/Upload/news/2017-01-23_094120.png', '<p><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0FsM2gcsu5AUs0gsxPvBoiccnWpLr6zEUXJl2VZJpniaCibnpJ4gAkDoFpOr2LdWHb4aELOfX79ibib7vI88dJ9SGg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近几个月以来，我县狠抓乡镇道路恢复改造工程建设，快速推进各项工程建设进度，有效提升乡镇道路交通承载能力，春节期间为各乡镇群众提供一个良好的出行环境。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0FsM2gcsu5AUs0gsxPvBoiccnWpLr6zEENJH09CvR6Bu3AV2tURHYb4Oh9HSyttLhkiaooAr3mv7xTAsgiaqCzKg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">记者在九龙、兴仁等乡镇发现，许多原先破损的路面都已经得到了修复，部分路段还能明显看到刚修复过的痕迹。不久前还在进行路面破碎开挖的国道</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">350水毁恢复工程袁市场镇段，如今也已经全部铺上了水稳层，工作人员正在对刚铺设好的路面进行清扫和养护。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0FsM2gcsu5AUs0gsxPvBoiccnWpLr6zE4PzZPHDIYX1fAfxfW6mCzDd5ZM9pEUOU9WibxjBsqTJ65RmXib6yD3MQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">随着春节临近，各地乡友纷纷回家过年，乡镇交通压力增大。县交通运输局组织精干力量，对涉及丰禾、九龙、袁市、石滓等</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">20多个乡镇的主要交通干线进行了恢复和改造，有力确保了春节期间各乡镇居民出行安全、舒适、畅通。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 23.2727px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">编辑：新媒体中心</span></strong></str