border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(图文来自邻水电视台）</span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><br/></p>', '1', null);
INSERT INTO `hf_local_hometown_reports` VALUES ('8', '1', '邻水：欢欢喜喜迎新年', '1', '2017-03-27 16:46:54', '9', '/Upload/news/2017-01-22_153017.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"EditorUpload/image/20170122/1485070133922263.jpg\" alt=\"邻水：欢欢喜喜迎新年\"/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\">市民正在选购春节用品。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">春节临近，市民开始忙着选购年画、春联、中国结、红灯笼等充满喜气的传统年货，增添节日喜庆氛围。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"EditorUpload/image/20170122/1485070134492500.jpg\" title=\"20170120153208047.jpg\"/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\">火红的灯笼带来浓浓的喜庆氛围。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"EditorUpload/image/20170122/1485070134298154.jpg\" title=\"怡墨书院的小志愿者为市民写春联。.jpg\"/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\">怡墨书院的小志愿者为市民写春联。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">邻水县城的大街小巷，处处洋溢着春节来临前的欢乐、祥和。（孔虹 刘苏阅）</p><p><br/></p>', '1', null);
