YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">会议通报了我县</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><font color=\"#3e3e3e\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">年的经济社会发展情况、组织人事工作和党风廉政建设工作</span></font><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 244, 244);\">。</span></font></span><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0FsM2gcsu5Vvjb5v59ONqd4OBe2UeR0vzht7NFukLg72BenzCPlNcc1okvu7ibYnQTAQ2tSdbuw3rKNrvicEYhA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 47px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 19px; background: rgb(254, 244, 244); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">会议指出，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 47px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 19px; background: rgb(254, 244, 244); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2016</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 47px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 19px; background: rgb(254, 244, 244); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年，面对复杂多变的经济形势和下行压力加大的考验，各党外人士围绕全县经济建设重点工作深入开展调查研究，主动履行社会责任，广泛参与社会管理创新，为加快建设作出了重要贡献。</span></span></font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 47px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 19px; background: rgb(254, 244, 244); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0FsM2gcsu5Vvjb5v59ONqd4OBe2UeR0OSNIhyOJ1ayWAHicoEwGW3EfHlibPR5Wib9YRHYJib2JqQ7TfibWPCEYCEA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></span></span></font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-he