xfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><section><section><section><section><section><p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(127, 119, 162); font-size: 22px; min-width: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px;\">背景资料</span></p></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;\">　　上海彩虹室内合唱团成立于2010年9月，是由上海音乐学院指挥系同学们组织成立，并逐渐吸收院内外热爱合唱人士的年轻音乐团体，是一个充满活力且快速成长着的、在合唱领域富有探索精神的团队。现任团长为指挥/作曲金承志先生，团员来自社会各界，从事各行各业，如投行职员、程序员、设计师、会计、人类学博士后、哲学研究者、美食博主、中小学教师、高校学生等等，唯一贯穿始终的是对合唱的热爱。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2016年1月，演唱旋律严肃、歌词戏谑的《张士超你到底把我家钥匙放在哪里了》而为大众熟知，成为了一个现象级的网络事件。 7月27日发布新作《感觉身体被掏空》，因以幽默口吻直指当下年轻人加班痛点而在网络被广泛传播。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.6;\">（来源“经济日报” ，综合“上海彩虹室内合唱团”微信、封面新闻）</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.6;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '1', null);
